txt.en: 'Hytbold only has two gates: one in the east and one in the west. Both of the gates still stand, but the timbers are burnt out and would not hold against any concerted assault. The West Gate must be replaced and rebuilt if we are to have any security.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
Bring the Tokens of Hytbold to Oseg
